 ('16', '16', 'en_us', 'Oiselle', '#ff5822', 'Brand Identity System', '<p class=\"large\">As they prepared to open their first bricks and mortar store, Oiselle&mdash;a pioneer in women’s running and athletic fashion&mdash;had a mature brand that needed an infusion of new energy. Turnstyle worked with the Oiselle team to establish an updated identity system and then applied it to a huge range of customer touch points, coordinated to deliver, install and deploy in concert with their store opening in Seattle’s University Village in the summer of 2015.</p>', 'AN\r\nINFUSION\r\nOF\r\nNEW\r\nENERGY', '#efefef', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-13 20:39:34', '2016-12-20 19:55:27', '0e3ab165-2609-406e-ad14-35ee38513a67'),
