 ('266', '122', '2', '1', 'en_us', '14', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Turnstyle Principal Juror for Comm Arts Design Annual\",\"slug\":\"turnstyle-principal-serves-as-juror-for-communication-arts-design-annual\",\"postDate\":1478209620,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"48\":{\"125\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffae96\",\"linkUrl\":\"\\/journal\",\"header\":\"I\\r\\nWanna\\r\\nRead\\r\\nMore\",\"subtext\":\"Our Journal\",\"fontColor\":\"#ffffff\"}}},\"29\":\"#daff00\",\"7\":[\"187\"],\"4\":\"#000000\",\"54\":[\"111\"],\"62\":[\"188\"],\"10\":{\"123\":{\"type\":\"centeredText\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"<p>Turnstyle principal and creative director Steven Watson was invited to serve as a juror for Communication Arts magazine\\u2019s 56th Annual Design Competition. Communication Arts is a professional journal for designers, art directors, design firms, corporate design departments, agencies and everyone involved in visual communications. The CA Design Annual, published each September,&nbsp;is one of the most respected competitions in our industry.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Of the 4,083 entries to the 56th Design Annual, only 153 were accepted, representing the work of 141 designers, design firms and in-house design departments, making the Design Annual the most exclusive major design competition in the world. Entries were selected on the basis of creative excellence and quality of execution.<\\/p>\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-1\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\"}},\"124\":{\"type\":\"insetImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"193\"],\"imageWidth\":\"50\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-1\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\"}},\"126\":{\"type\":\"centeredText\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"<p>Steve screened entries along with five other jurors: Kelly Bjork (VSA Partners), Dora Drimalas (Hybrid-Design), Jay Fle