 ('271', '118', '2', '1', 'en_us', '6', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"We\'re Building Our Own Building\",\"slug\":\"were-building-our-own-building\",\"postDate\":1478209380,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"29\":\"#ffffff\",\"7\":[\"190\"],\"4\":\"#000000\",\"54\":[\"111\"],\"62\":[\"191\"],\"10\":{\"119\":{\"type\":\"centeredText\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"<p>Together with our brand strategy partners at&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/stokestrategy.com\\/\\\">Stoke,<\\/a>&nbsp;Turnstyle is breaking ground on a new 5,000 sq. foot office in August 2016. The building will serve as home for 20+ strategists, designers and developers. Located on Canal Street, the park-side project borders the Burke-Gilman Trail and overlooks the Fremont Cut waterway. &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\\"The firms continue to grow, and our need for space was at odds with the long-term lease trends of Seattle,\\u201d said Stoke partner Erin Quick. \\u201cIt makes good financial sense for the businesses, and for the firms\\u2019 practices. We\\u2019re creating a unique place where creative thinkers can do their best work, and clients can collaborate with us in new and different ways.\\u201d<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>On the street level, a cafe-style collaboration space serves as a foundation to two levels with open-floor studios and meeting space. Designed with 16\\u2019 floor-to-ceiling windows, the plan takes advantage of the views over the trail and canal.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u201cThe work areas will be bathed with natural light. An open atrium at the center creates visual interest, with the benefit of passive solar design,\\u201d said Ben Graham, partner at Turnstyle. \\u201cIt\'s a design-friendly environment that makes the best of our open, collaborative work style.\\u201d&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u201cThe commercial office market is racing, and the long-term value for buyers in Seattle looks good,\\u201d noted Graham. \\u201cAs the business environment accelerates, having a place that minimizes our commutes, offers easy access to downtown, with everyday access to great restaurants, and enhances mobility options on the Burke-Gilman Trail \\u2013 all with a deck and a view \\u2013 seemed like a winning combination.\\u201d<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The architecture was led by award-winning&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/heliotropearchitects.com\\/\\\">Heliotrope,<\\/a>&nbsp;of Ballard. Seattle\\u2019s&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/westernventures.com\\/\\\">Western Ventures<\\/a>serves as the general contractor.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Construction is targeted for completion in June, 2017.<\\/p>\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-0\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\"}}}}}', '2016-11-23 00:14:53', '2016-11-23 00:14:53', '3e64d535-5e40-49c3-9573-f116db3ef83d'),
 ('272', '15', '3', '1', 'en_us', '79', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Justin Golmer\",\"slug\":\"justin-golmer-promo\",\"postDate\":1476391140,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"14\":[{\"col1\":\"Recogonition\",\"col2\":\"Print Regional Design Annual 2015\"}],\"3\":[\"12\"],\"29\":\"#efefef\",\"9\":\"Wake up\\r\\nStyle\\r\\nshoot\\r\\ndo it all\\r\\nagain\",\"7\":[\"177\"],\"4\":\"#ffae96\",\"8\":\"<p class=\\\"large\\\">Justin Gollmer, one of our go-to photography partners, asked us design a ten-year retrospective promotional brochure. Wake, Style, Shoot, Do It All Again is a collection of images highlighting his work behind, beside, and around the camera. The brochure is divided into four sections that blur the lines between Gollmer\\u2019s personal and commercial work: people, action, travel, and product. Short sheets bound to the exterior provide thumbnail image guides to each section with captions for each image.<\\/p>\",\"62\":[\"184\"],\"10\":{\"28\":{\"type\":\"largeImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"177\"],\"layoutOptions\":\"full-width\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-0\"}},\"41\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"vimeoVideoId\":\"172827555\",\"autoplay\":\"1\",\"framed\":\"1\"}},\"31\":{\"type\":\"insetImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"179\"],\"imageWidth\":\"50\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-2\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#d6ff2e\"}},\"53\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"vimeoVideoId\":\"172827555\",\"autoplay\":\"1\",\"framed\":\"\"}},\"134\":{\"type\":\"imageWithDescription\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"179\"],\"imageWidth\":\"50\",\"description\":\"<p>Subtitle<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Donec id elit non mi porta gravida at eget metus. Fusce dapibus, tellus ac cursus commodo, tortor mauris condimentum nibh, ut fermentum massa justo sit amet risus. Etiam porta sem malesuada magna m