 ('319', '101', '10', '1', 'en_us', '37', '', '{\"typeId\":\"11\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Studio\",\"slug\":\"studio\",\"postDate\":1478129954,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"48\":{\"102\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"backgroundImage\":[\"97\"],\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"linkUrl\":\"\\/contact\",\"header\":\"Drop \\r\\nus \\r\\na \\r\\nline\",\"subtext\":\"Contact Us\",\"fontColor\":\"#efefef\"}}},\"46\":\"<p class=\\\"large\\\">Born in 2004<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\">We are a full-service creative agency with offices in Seattle and Portland. A dedicated team of designers, strategists, developers and account specialists, we create highly-crafted brand experiences that clarify purpose, encourage action, and inspire brand loyalty. We\\u2019d love to get to know you and help tell your story.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"10\":{\"103\":{\"type\":\"carousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"197\",\"198\",\"196\",\"199\"],\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-2\"}},\"104\":{\"type\":\"twoColumnContent\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"leftColumn\":\"<p class=\\\"h3 med\\\"><span class=\\\"white\\\">STYLE<br>IS A<br>SIMPLE<br>WAY<br>OF<br>SAYING<br>COMPLEX<br>THINGS<br><\\/span><span class=\\\"blue\\\">&mdash;JEAN<br>COCTEAU<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"rightColumn\":\"<p class=\\\"large\\\"><span class=\\\"white\\\"><span><\\/span>Style is Not a&nbsp;4-letter Word<span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\"><span class=\\\"white\\\"><span><\\/span>In our experience, the brands that are the most magnetic are those which project distinct, memorable and charismatic personalities. These brands place equal emphasis on what they say and how they say it. Some design purists might say that style is merely artificial decoration that should be avoided in favor of logic&mdash;\\u201cform follows function\\u201d and all that. Don\\u2019t get us wrong, we\\u2019re not proponents of style for its own sake, or as ornament applied after an idea has already been defined. Rather, we employ style as an integral and strategic component of our brand-development process. At its best, style can be that magical something about a company or product that pulls people in and transcends the logical. So, to us, style is not a 4-letter word. On the contrary, we embrace it, harnessing its power to cut through the clutter.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\"><span class=\\\"white\\\">And besides, \\u201cstyle\\u201d has five letters.<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-2\"}},\"106\":{\"type\":\"twoColumnContent\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"leftColumn\":\"<p class=\\\"large\\\"><span class=\\\"white\\\">We Do<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"rightColumn\":\"<p class=\\\"h2 caps white\\\"><a href=\\\"\\/strategy\\\">Strategy<\\/a><br><a href=\\\"\\/identity\\\">Identity<\\/a><br><a href=\\\"\\/digital\\\">Digital<\\/a><br><a href=\\\"\\/print\\\">Print<\\/a><br><a href=\\\"\\/packaging\\\">Packaging<\\/a><br><a href=\\\"\\/environment\\\">Environment<\\/a><\\/p>\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-2\"}},\"107\":{\"type\":\"twoColumnContent\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"leftColumn\":\"<p class=\\\"h3 caps\\\">OUR<br>CLIENTS<br>&<br>INDUSTRIES<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"h3 caps\\\"><\\/p>\",\"rightColumn\":\"\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-1\"}},\"108\":{\"type\":\"twoColumnContent\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"leftColumn\":\"<p class=\\\"large\\\"><span class=\\\"gray\\\">Industry<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"h3 caps\\\">TEAGUE<br>NIKE<br>STARBUCKS<br>MICROSOFT<br>AMAZON<br>AIGA<br>NORDSTROM<br>TEAGUE<br>NIKE<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\"><span class=\\\"gray\\\">Industry<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"h3 caps\\\">TEAGUE<br>NIKE<br>STARBUCKS<br>MICROSOFT<br>AMAZON<br>AIGA<br>NORDSTROM<br>TEAGUE<br>NIKE<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\"><span class=\\\"gray\\\">Industry<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"h3 caps\\\">TEAGUE<br>NIKE<br>STARBUCKS<br>MICROSOFT<br>AMAZON<br>AIGA<br>NORDSTROM<br>TEAGUE<br>NIKE<\\/p>\",\"rightColumn\":\"<p class=\\\"large\\\"><span class=\\\"gray\\\">Industry<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"h3 caps\\\">TEAGUE<br>NIKE<br>STARBUCKS<br>MICROSOFT<br>AMAZON<br>AIGA<br>NORDSTROM<br>TEAGUE<br>NIKE<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\"><span class=\\\"gray\\\">Industry<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"h3 caps\\\">TEAGUE<br>NIKE<br>STARBUCKS<br>MICROSOFT<br>AMAZON<br>AIGA<br>NORDSTROM<br>TEAGUE<br>NIKE<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\"><span class=\\\"gray\\\">Industry<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"h3 caps\\\">TEAGUE<br>NIKE<br>STARBUCKS<br>MICROSOFT<br>AMAZON<br>AIGA<br>NORDSTROM<br>TEAGUE<br>NIKE<\\/p>\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-1\"}}},\"47\":\"<p class=\\\"large\\\">08\\/2016 &mdash; IdN Magazine v23n2<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\">06\\/2016 &mdash; Communication Arts Design Annual 2016<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\">05\\/2016 &mdash; PRINT Magazine Regional Design Annual 2016<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\">03\\/2016 &mdash; Communication Arts Design Annual 2015<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\">02\\/2016 &mdash; IdN Magazine v23n2<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\">12\\/2015 &mdash; Communication Arts Design Annual 2016<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\">10\\/2015 &mdash; PRINT Magazine Regional Design Annual 2016<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\">10\\/2015 &mdash; Communication Arts Design Annual 2015<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\">06\\/2015 &mdash; PRINT Magazine Regional Design Annual 2016<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\">02\\/2015 &mdash; Communication Arts Design Annual 2015<\\/p>\",\"44\":\"MEET\\r\\nOUR\\r\\nTALENTED\\r\\nTEAM\"}}', '2016-12-01 22:50:38', '2016-12-01 22:50:38', '553cf406-6599-4cab-bc22-a451d8c1b29d'),
 ('320', '201', '3', '46', 'en_us', '31', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"46\",\"title\":\"Turnstyle Case Study Guide\",\"slug\":\"turnstyle-case-study-guide\",\"postDate\":1479938460,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"14\":[{\"col1\":\"Category Heading\",\"col2\":\"Additional Info\"},{\"col1\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\"}],\"3\":[\"11\",\"12\",\"13\"],\"29\":\"#ffffff\",\"9\":\"HERO\\r\\nHEADLINE\\r\\nWITH LINE\\r\\nBREAKS\",\"7\":[\"204\"],\"4\":\"#3c00ff\",\"8\":\"<p class=\\\"large\\\">Welcome to the case study guide! Please don\'t delete me. When the time comes, we can turn me off, but until then I shall exist. Within this guide you will find information about the modules, color, typography, image optimization, file naming and more.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\">The area at right is dynamically populated with information from the CMS. The client comes from the title&nbsp;field, and the disciplines can be added one at a time depending on the particular project. Additional fields can be added and customized for things like URLs, Awards &&nbsp;Press, and other things unique to particular projects.<\\/p>\",\"62\":[\"203\"],\"10\":{\"211\":{\"type\":\"centeredText\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"<p class=\\\"large\\\"><span class=\\\"white\\\">The Modules (this is the Centered Text module)<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\"><span class=\\\"white\\\">Below are all the modules in the CMS, with accompanying image sizing and other specs. There are several variables available to each module, some have more than others. You can specify vertical spacing (padding), background color, image\\/text orientation, full width vs framed, etc. Each module has a unique set of components one can set. Image modules have the image sizes specified in the CMS with the associated field.<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-3\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\"}},\"212\":{\"type\":\"largeImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"213\"],\"layoutOptions\":\"full-width\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-0\"}},\"219\":{\"type\":\"largeImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"213\"],\"layoutOptions\":\"framed\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-1\"}},\"215\":{\"type\":\"insetImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"214\"],\"imageWidth\":\"50\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-3\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\"}},\"216\":{\"type\":\"imageWithDescription\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"214\"],\"imageWidth\":\"75\",\"description\":\"<p class=\\\"large\\\">This is the Image with Description module. The text orientation (left\\/right), background color and&nbsp;vertical spacing is variable.<\\/p>\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-3\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#efefef\"}},\"218\":{\"type\":\"twoUpImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"leftImage\":[\"221\"],\"rightImage\":[\"217\"],\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-1\"}},\"235\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"vimeoEmbedUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/player.vimeo.com\\/external\\/112934911.sd.mp4?s=a11efd4f0191a7846bc17eeba07e1739e031775d&profile_id=112\",\"posterImage\":[\"236\"],\"autoplay\":\"\",\"framed\":\"\"}},\"237\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"vimeoEmbedUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/player.vimeo.com\\/external\\/112936935.sd.mp4?s=ec74a18135c1f7a0b6fceafd06c4cafd448d0cbb&profile_id=165\",\"posterImage\":\"\",\"autoplay\":\"1\",\"framed\":\"1\"}},\"222\":{\"type\":\"centeredText\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"<p class=\\\"large\\\"><span class=\\\"white\\\">There is also a carousel module. The carousel module is being dialed in and spec\'s aren\'t available. It isn\'t something we\'d intended to be a widely used case study&nbsp;component anyway. Keep on scrolling for color, type, file naming, etc.<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-3\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\"}},\"208\":{\"type\":\"imageWithDescription\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"position\":\"right\",\"image\":[\"207\"],\"imageWidth\":\"75\",\"description\":\"<p class=\\\"large\\\">Color Palette<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\">All type on the site is off-white or off-black. When designating a type color for the hero area, select one of those two.&nbsp;Background colors & highlight colors can be uniquely specified based on the color palette of a particular project, or for dramatic effect!<\\/p>\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-2\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\"}},\"224\":{\"type\":\"imageWithDescription\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"223\"],\"imageWidth\":\"75\",\"description\":\"<p class=\\\"large\\\">Image Types<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\">The CMS&nbsp;will accept just about any image format (JPEG, GIF, PNG, SVG, etc). It is important that our site perform well and look great \\u2013 so there are particular instances where using an SVG may be preferred to a transparent PNG, for icons, logos, etc. The image&nbsp;at left is example of an SVG.<\\/p>\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-2\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\"}},\"226\":{\"type\":\"imageWithDescription\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"position\":\"right\",\"image\":[\"225\"],\"imageWidth\":\"100\",\"description\":\"<p class=\\\"large\\\">Image Optimization<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\">The majority of the images we upload into our CMS will be JPEGs. JPEGs can get large, and we want to keep the file size down to optimize performance. ALL JPEG images should be optimized with the JPEG High preset. The Quality should be set to 60% and Progressive should be checked.<\\/p>\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-2\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\"}},\"230\":{\"type\":\"imageWithDescription\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"227\"],\"imageWidth\":\"75\",\"description\":\"<p class=\\\"large\\\">File Naming<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\">File naming should be consistent across all entries. For common, required&nbsp;elements, such as the Hero Image and the List Image (thumbnail), a common convention should be adhered to. For all other images, use an appropriate description of the content of the image.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\">All file names should be lowercase, with hyphens separating descriptors, followed by a number. Serial and alternate&nbsp;images should use the same name and the next number, -01, -02, etc.<\\/p>\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-2\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\"}}},\"6\":\"Project Title\"}}', '2016-12-06 00:53:16', '2016-12-06 00:53:16', '36560901-c8cd-4626-9dec-9e5c655e3f7f'),
