lds\":{\"image\":[\"213\"],\"layoutOptions\":\"full-width\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-0\"}},\"219\":{\"type\":\"largeImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"213\"],\"layoutOptions\":\"framed\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-1\"}},\"215\":{\"type\":\"insetImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"214\"],\"imageWidth\":\"50\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-3\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\"}},\"216\":{\"type\":\"imageWithDescription\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"214\"],\"imageWidth\":\"75\",\"description\":\"<p class=\\\"large\\\">This is the Image with Description module. The text orientation (left\\/right), background color and&nbsp;vertical spacing is variable.<\\/p>\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-3\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#efefef\"}},\"218\":{\"type\":\"twoUpImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"leftImage\":[\"221\"],\"rightImage\":[\"217\"],\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-1\"}},\"243\":{\"type\":\"largeImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"242\"],\"layoutOptions\":\"full-width\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-0\"}},\"235\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"vimeoEmbedUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/player.vimeo.com\\/external\\/112934911.sd.mp4?s=a11efd4f0191a7846bc17eeba07e1739e031775d&profile_id=112\",\"posterImage\":[\"236\"],\"autoplay\":\"\",\"framed\":\"\"}},\"237\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"vimeoEmbedUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/player.vimeo.com\\/external\\/112936935.sd.mp4?s=ec74a18135c1f7a0b6fceafd06c4cafd448d0cbb&profile_id=165\",\"posterImage\":\"\",\"autoplay\":\"1\",\"framed\":\"1\"}},\"222\":{\"type\":\"centeredText\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"<p class=\\\"large\\\"><span class=\\\"white\\\">There is also a carousel module. The carousel module is being dialed in and spec\'s aren\'t available. It isn\'t something we\'d intended to be a widely used case study&nbsp;component anyway. Keep on scrolling for color, type, file naming, etc.<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-3\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\"}},\"208\":{\"type\":\"imageWithDescription\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"position\":\"right\",\"image\":[\"207\"],\"imageWidth\":\"75\",\"description\":\"<p class=\\\"large\\\">Color Palette<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\">All type on the site is off-white or off-black. When designating a type color for the hero area, select one of those two.&nbsp;Background colors & highlight colors can be uniquely specified based on the color palette of a particular project, or for dramatic effect!<\\/p>\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-2\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\"}},\"224\":{\"type\":\"imageWithDescription\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"223\"],\"imageWidth\":\"75\",\"description\":\"<p class=\\\"large\\\">Image Types<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\">The CMS&nbsp;will accept just about any image format (JPEG, GIF, PNG, SVG, etc). It is important that our site perform well and look great \\u2013 so there are particular instances where using an SVG may be preferred to a transparent PNG, for icons, logos, etc. The image&nbsp;at left is example of an SVG.<\\/p>\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-2\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\"}},\"226\":{\"type\":\"imageWithDescription\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"position\":\"right\",\"image\":[\"225\"],\"imageWidth\":\"100\",\"description\":\"<p class=\\\"large\\\">Image Optimization<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\">The majority of the images we upload into our CMS will be JPEGs. JPEGs can get large, and we want to keep the file size down to optimize performance. ALL JPEG images should be optimized with the JPEG High preset. The Quality should be set to 60% and Progressive should be checked.<\\/p>\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-2\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\"}},\"230\":{\"type\":\"imageWithDescription\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"227\"],\"imageWidth\":\"75\",\"description\":\"<p class=\\\"large\\\">File Naming<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\">File naming should be consistent across all entries. For common, required&nbsp;elements, such as the Hero Image and the List Image (thumbnail), a common convention should be adhered to. For all other images, use an appropriate description of the content of the image.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\">All file names should be lowercase, with hyphens separating descriptors, followed by a number. Serial and alternate&nbsp;images should use the same name and the next number, -01, -02, etc.<\\/p>\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-2\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\"}}},\"6\":\"Project Title\"}}', '2016-12-06 22:39:24', '2016-12-06 22:39:24', 'aaf475d7-4d74-445d-8229-fcf243c0e63e'),
