 ('328', '201', '3', '1', 'en_us', '37', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"46\",\"title\":\"Turnstyle\",\"slug\":\"turnstyle-case-study-guide\",\"postDate\":1479938460,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"14\":[{\"col1\":\"Category Heading\",\"col2\":\"Additional Info\"},{\"col1\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\"}],\"3\":[\"11\",\"12\",\"13\"],\"29\":\"#ffffff\",\"9\":\"HERO\\r\\nHEADLINE\\r\\nWITH LINE\\r\\nBREAKS\",\"7\":[\"244\"],\"4\":\"#3c00ff\",\"8\":\"<p class=\\\"large\\\">Welcome to the case study guide! Please don\'t delete me. When the time comes, we can turn me off, but until then I shall exist. Within this guide you will find information about the modules, color, typography, image optimization, file naming and more.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\">The area at right is dynamically populated with information from the CMS. The client comes from the title&nbsp;field, and the disciplines can be added one at a time depending on the particular project. Additional fields can be added and customized for things like URLs, Awards &&nbsp;Press, and other things unique to particular projects.<\\/p>\",\"62\":[\"203\"],\"10\":{\"211\":{\"type\":\"centeredText\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"<p class=\\\"large\\\"><span class=\\\"white\\\">The Modules (this is the Centered Text module)<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\"><span class=\\\"white\\\">Below are all the modules in the CMS, with accompanying image sizing and other specs. There are several variables available to each module, some have more than others. You can specify vertical spacing (padding), background color, image\\/text orientation, full width vs framed, etc. Each module has a unique set of components one can set. Image modules have the image sizes specified in the CMS with the associated field.<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"spacingTop\":\"spacing-top-2\",\"spacingBottom\":\"spacing-bottom-2\"}},\"212\":{\"type\":\"largeImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\"