 ('428', '44', '6', '46', 'en_us', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Journal\",\"slug\":\"journal\",\"postDate\":1476834521,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"48\":{\"192\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#3c00ff\",\"linkUrl\":\"\\/work\",\"header\":\"See \\r\\nOur\\r\\nWork\",\"subtext\":\"See Our Work\",\"fontColor\":\"#efefef\"}}}}}', '2016-12-20 19:10:49', '2016-12-20 19:10:49', '03c51c38-9328-4ea2-a09c-a7d0e59a440b'),
 ('429', '101', '10', '46', 'en_us', '44', '', '{\"typeId\":\"11\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Studio\",\"slug\":\"studio\",\"postDate\":1478129954,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"48\":{\"102\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"backgroundImage\":[\"97\"],\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"linkUrl\":\"\\/contact\",\"header\":\"Drop \\r\\nus \\r\\na \\r\\nline\",\"subtext\":\"Contact Us\",\"fontColor\":\"#efefef\"}}},\"46\":\"<p class=\\\"large\\\">Born in 2004<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\">We are a full-service creative agency with offices in Seattle and Portland. A dedicated team of designers, strategists, developers and account specialists, we create highly-crafted brand experiences that clarify purpose, encourage action, and inspire brand loyalty. We\\u2019d love to get to know you and help tell your story.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"10\":{\"103\":{\"type\":\"carousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"197\",\"198\",\"196\",\"199\"],\"spacingTop\":\"spacing-top-0\",\"spacingBottom\":\"spacing-bottom-1\"}},\"104\":{\"type\":\"twoColumnContent\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"leftColumn\":\"<p class=\\\"h3 med\\\"><span class=\\\"white\\\">STYLE<br>IS A<br>SIMPLE<br>WAY<br>OF<br>SAYING<br>COMPLEX<br>THINGS<br><\\/span><span class=\\\"blue\\\">&mdash;JEAN<br>COCTEAU<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"rightColumn\":\"<p class=\\\"large\\\"><span class=\\\"white\\\"><span><\\/span>Style is Not a&nbsp;4-letter Word<span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\"><span class=\\\"white\\\"><span><\\/span>In our experience, the brands that are the most magnetic are those which project distinct, memorable and charismatic personalities. These brands place equal emphasis on what they say and how they say it. Some design purists might say that style is merely artificial decoration that should be avoided in favor of logic&mdash;\\u201cform follows function\\u201d and all that. Don\\u2019t get us wrong, we\\u2019re not proponents of style for its own sake, or as ornament applied after an idea has already been defined. Rather, we employ style as an integral and strategic component of our brand-development process. At its best, style can be that magical something about a company or product that pulls people in and transcends the logical. So, to us, style is not a 4-letter word. On the contrary, we embrace it, harnessing its power to cut through the clutter.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\"><span class=\\\"white\\\">And besides, \\u201cstyle\\u201d has five letters.<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"spacingTop\":\"spacing-top-2\",\"spacingBottom\":\"spacing-bottom-0\"}},\"106\":{\"type\":\"twoColumnContent\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"leftColumn\":\"<p class=\\\"large\\\"><span class=\\\"white\\\">We Do<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"rightColumn\":\"<p class=\\\"h2 caps\\\"><a href=\\\"\\/strategy\\\">Strategy<\\/a><br><a href=\\\"\\/identity\\\">Identity<\\/a><br><a href=\\\"\\/digital\\\">Digital<\\/a><br><a href=\\\"\\/print\\\">Print<\\/a><br><a href=\\\"\\/packaging\\\">Packaging<\\/a><br><a href=\\\"\\/environment\\\">Environment<\\/a><\\/p>\",\"spacingTop\":\"spacing-top-2\",\"spacingBottom\":\"spacing-bottom-1\"}},\"107\":{\"type\":\"twoColumnContent\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"leftColumn\":\"<p class=\\\"h3 caps\\\">OUR<br>CLIENTS<br>&<br>INDUSTRIES<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"h3 caps\\\"><\\/p>\",\"rightColumn\":\"\",\"spacingTop\":\"spacing-top-2\",\"spacingBottom\":\"spacing-bottom-0\"}},\"108\":{\"type\":\"twoColumnContent\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"leftColumn\":\"<p class=\\\"large\\\"><span class=\\\"gray\\\">Industry<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"h3 caps\\\">TEAGUE<br>NIKE<br>STARBUCKS<br>MICROSOFT<br>AMAZON<br>AIGA<br>NORDSTROM<br>TEAGUE<br>NIKE<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\"><span class=\\\"gray\\\">Industry<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"h3 caps\\\">TEAGUE<b