 ('43', '208', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'right', '<p class=\"large\">Color Palette</p>\r\n<p class=\"large\">All type on the site is off-white or off-black. When designating a type color for the hero area, select one of those two.&nbsp;Background colors & highlight colors can be uniquely specified based on the color palette of a particular project, or for dramatic effect!</p>', 'spacing-top-2', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '75', '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'spacing-bottom-2', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-11-23 22:31:29', '2016-12-20 19:55:11', 'ae9ff83d-337f-426b-a883-c90efd53f6cc'),
 ('44', '211', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p class=\"large\"><span class=\"white\">The Modules (this is the Centered Text module)</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"large\"><span class=\"white\">Below are all the modules in the CMS, with accompanying image sizing and other specs. There are several variables available to each module, some have more than others. You can specify vertical spacing (padding), background color, image/text orientation, full width vs framed, etc. Each module has a unique set of components one can set. Image modules have the image sizes specified in the CMS with the associated field.</span></p>', 'spacing-top-2', NULL, '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'spacing-bottom-2', NULL, NULL, '2016-11-23 22:49:35', '2016-12-20 19:55:11', '263e57c5-a766-4cf3-bbe0-d2e302db30c2'),
